		<title>Innovative Strategy Closes the Achievement Gap on Chicago’s West Side</title>
		<link>https://www.breakthrough.org/innovative-strategy-closes-the-achievement-gap-on-chicagos-west-side/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 09 Oct 2018 01:00:11 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dr. Marcie Curry]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Vision Shapers]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Education & Youth Development]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Nettie Bailey Student Achievement Program]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[London Johnson Arts & Technology Academy]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Youth]]></category>
