		<description><![CDATA[<p>The Breakthrough Young Professionals Board welcomed scores of emerging leaders to the “Aspire: Finding Meaning In Work” panel discussion and networking reception at Jenner &#038; Block in downtown Chicago last week. The largest Aspire crowd to date was guided through a conversation of how to balance a busy work-life schedule with the value of staying involved in our communities through advocacy and volunteering.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.breakthrough.org/aspire-finding-meaning-in-your-work/">Aspire: Finding Meaning In Your Work</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.breakthrough.org">Breakthrough</a>.</p>
